{"tid":1386532,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"爭取民意、國際支持，唔好進攻、還擊","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T17:33:14.000Z","uid":173326,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3cd85d701b0485fd2b6aea327c2e958ea8c4869b","tid":1386532,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:09:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">睇埋下面先</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bZrWqF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bZrWqF.gif&h=e9acd895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QZQrxuh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQZQrxuh.gif&h=e8894b85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oq12Qho.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOq12Qho.gif&h=0b0f27fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8UOTWV1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8UOTWV1.gif&h=29319b79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQQWagB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQQWagB.gif&h=67e696b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PbWFBUW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPbWFBUW.jpg&h=976d5904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HMUPveV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHMUPveV.jpg&h=7f739787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N5jLxRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5jLxRG.png&h=3c0228a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>你地睇完有乜感覺？我嬲到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而家黑警棍棍打頭、槍槍瞄頭，明顯係想殺抗爭者。<br />\n唔止抗爭者，連其他路過嘅市民、記者都唔放過！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警黑勾結，連法官都係佢地嘅人。跟和平嘅途徑根本咩都做唔到，只會捱打、捱子彈、捱黑獄！<br />\n所謂嘅國際社會只會講兩句同情下你，唔會出兵幫你，因為佢地仲要同中國做生意發大財！</span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>如果你仍然堅信要保持被動捱打唔進攻，唔緊要，唔該請你先去最前擋一粒海綿彈先再思考</ins>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地要嘅係贏呀！唔係白白流血！<br />\n輸左嘅話會大規模清算、香港變成64後嘅大陸！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins>連為大家犧牲、堅信大家會贏會救佢地出嚟嘅嘅義士都會永遠不見天日，甚至被送中做李旺陽2.0</ins>！！！</span><br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"ef4c7ab83cb86ada9b0e19efa33f18f72730ce65","tid":1386532,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c907419baec49af8d8c1b8d77e24ea3d663a726","tid":1386532,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d5dcb87f604ec26b10dda35521e4f654e3241e","tid":1386532,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:29:17.000Z","msg":"醒下啦，民意撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682407046fe66820c0b080ca0179f5405f0ce6bf","tid":1386532,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e13ef923344129f2fd8842ba97a3eb9f18f544e","tid":1386532,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54272c265dee1ed134aa65e3abe5653247ec4a0","tid":1386532,"uid":293767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:42:52.000Z","msg":"學術討論:市民有無得告政府?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386803</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n👆🏻👆🏻👆🏻👆🏻要政府同黑警負責"},{"pid":"7431d5019a75ef59b3f1e5